{"title": "Miscellaneous & Tricks", "source": "internal-att", "source_label": "InternalAllTheThings", "path": "cheatsheets/miscellaneous-tricks", "html": "<h1 id=\"miscellaneous-tricks\">Miscellaneous &amp; Tricks</h1>\n<p>All the tricks that couldn't be classified somewhere else.</p>\n<h2 id=\"send-messages-to-other-users\">Send Messages to Other Users</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Windows</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nb\">PS </span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"p\">:\\&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">msg</span> <span class=\"n\">Swissky</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">SERVER</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">CRASHLAB</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Stop rebooting the XXXX service !&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">PS </span><span class=\"n\">C</span><span class=\"p\">:\\&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">msg</span> <span class=\"p\">*</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">V</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">W</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">SERVER</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"n\">CRASHLAB</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Hello all !&quot;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>Linux</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">wall</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;Stop messing with the XXX service !&quot;</span>\n<span class=\"n\">wall</span> <span class=\"n\">-n</span> <span class=\"s2\">&quot;System will go down for 2 hours maintenance at 13:00 PM&quot;</span>  <span class=\"c\"># &quot;-n&quot; only for root</span>\n<span class=\"n\">who</span>\n<span class=\"nb\">write </span><span class=\"n\">root</span> <span class=\"n\">pts</span><span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">2</span> <span class=\"c\"># press Ctrl+D  after typing the message. </span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"netexec-credential-database\">NetExec Credential Database</h2>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">nxcdb</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">default</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">workspace</span> <span class=\"n\">create</span> <span class=\"n\">test</span>\n<span class=\"n\">nxcdb</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">test</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">workspace</span> <span class=\"k\">default</span>\n<span class=\"n\">nxcdb</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">test</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">proto</span> <span class=\"n\">smb</span>\n<span class=\"n\">nxcdb</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">test</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"n\">smb</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">creds</span>\n<span class=\"n\">nxcdb</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">test</span><span class=\"p\">)(</span><span class=\"n\">smb</span><span class=\"p\">)</span> <span class=\"p\">&gt;</span> <span class=\"n\">export</span> <span class=\"n\">creds</span> <span class=\"n\">csv</span> <span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">tmp</span><span class=\"p\">/</span><span class=\"n\">creds</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>NetExec workspaces</p>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"c\"># get current workspace</span>\n<span class=\"n\">poetry</span> <span class=\"n\">run</span> <span class=\"n\">nxcdb</span> <span class=\"n\">-gw</span> \n\n<span class=\"c\"># create workspace</span>\n<span class=\"n\">poetry</span> <span class=\"n\">run</span> <span class=\"n\">nxcdb</span> <span class=\"n\">-cw</span> <span class=\"n\">testing</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\"># set workspace</span>\n<span class=\"n\">poetry</span> <span class=\"n\">run</span> <span class=\"n\">nxcdb</span> <span class=\"n\">-sw</span> <span class=\"n\">testing</span> \n</code></pre></div>", "excerpt": "Miscellaneous &amp; Tricks All the tricks that couldn't be classified somewhere else. Send Messages to Other Users Windows PS C :\\&gt; msg Swissky / SERVER : CRASHLAB &quot;Stop rebooting the XXXX service !&quot; PS C :\\&gt; msg * / V / W / SERVER :…", "tags": []}